                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/gizonazale/">gizonazale</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2010-03-24</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">好书一本，写得很详尽，而且结合西方哲学进行比较~而且译者也很难得，非常准确地把握诸多梵语哲学名词对译，赞一个！</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

